- npm vite@latest
- npm install
- npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer
- npx tailwindcss init -p
- create global.css with @tailwind base, utilities and components
- import global at App.tsx;
- config tailwind.config.cjs; 
- Component library:    npm install @radix-ui/react-dialog
                        npm install @radix-ui/react-popover
- instal library to work with conditionals inside the CSS Class: npm install clsx